      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIDNIGHT HOYEON (1) goes very well this trip starting six times for two wins and three minors. Placed last time (26.43) at Bulli in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 6 lengths. Rates on top and should go close. TAMMY ROAD (7) finds it hard to win. Finished third (35.21) at Gosford latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Expected to be in the finish again. KABAYEL (2) was a last start winner (30.29) from Box 6 at this track. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Leading player again. TERRA MAY (8) picked up a cheque last time and is in the mix again.",
